            </div>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-emerald-500/20 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-black text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-wider">
              Active
            </span>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-5">
            <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-white/10 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wide">
              Demolition Derby Platform
            </span>
          </div>

          <p class="text-base text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Run your derby like a pro. The complete platform for demolition derby event management. Registration, payments, live timing, and results — all in one place.
          </p>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-300 font-bold">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path
